		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2><br><br>              Self-service<br>             Kiosks<br><br></h2>		
			<h3>PowerTank kiosks</h3>		
		<p>This is one of the best examples demonstrating the simple yet powerful impacts of design thinking in service design.</p><p>This self-service product can charge up to 14 digital devices at the same time and all the bays have colourful lightings showing the status of the device battery. </p><p>Also we designed a unique digital signage display at the top of the kiosk to stream videos on-demand.</p><p>You can order any custom designed self-service platforms like this to improve your customer satisfaction.</p>		
															<img width="750" height="950" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/powertank-1.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/powertank-1.png 750w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/powertank-1-237x300.png 237w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" />															
			<h3>Macro kiosks</h3>		
		<p>These are minimal yet iconic piece of hardware specifically designed for multi-purpose everyday applications like self ordering, self check-ins, information apps and more.</p><p>We can custom design all kiosk platforms according your needs and your brand identity and these can be free-standing or wall-mounted as well.</p><p>You can order any custom designed self-service platforms like this to improve your customer satisfaction.</p>		
															<img width="750" height="950" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Macro-kiosks-1.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Macro-kiosks-1.png 750w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Macro-kiosks-1-237x300.png 237w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" />															
			<h3>Mini kiosks</h3>		
		<p>This project as about even more minimizing kiosk footprint in orderto gain more value per area for self-service platforms.</p><p>You can order any custom designed self-service platforms like this to improve your customer satisfaction.</p>		
															<img width="750" height="950" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Mini-kiosks-1.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Mini-kiosks-1.png 750w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Mini-kiosks-1-237x300.png 237w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" />															
			<figure><a href="https://moonshire.co.uk/apps/"><img width="300" height="142" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Apps-slide-1-300x142.png" alt="" loading="lazy" /></a></figure><h3><a href="https://moonshire.co.uk/apps/">Self-service Apps</a></h3>		
			<figure><a href="https://moonshire.co.uk/kiosks/"><img width="300" height="244" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Kiosks-three-2-300x244.png" alt="" loading="lazy" /></a></figure><h3><a href="https://moonshire.co.uk/kiosks/">Self-service Kiosks</a></h3>		
			<figure><a href="https://moonshire.co.uk/design/"><img width="300" height="212" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/design-back-pink-1-300x212.png" alt="" loading="lazy" /></a></figure><h3><a href="https://moonshire.co.uk/design/">Self-service Design</a></h3>]]></content:encoded>

			<h2>Carwash EPoS app</h2>		
			<h2>Select and pay</h2>		
								<figure><img src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Carwash-04.jpg" alt="Carwash-04" /></figure><figure><img src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Carwash-05.jpg" alt="Carwash-05" /></figure><figure><img src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Carwash-06.jpg" alt="Carwash-06" /></figure><figure><img src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Carwash-07.jpg" alt="Carwash-07" /></figure><figure><img src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Carwash-08.jpg" alt="Carwash-08" /></figure><figure><img src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Carwash-09.jpg" alt="Carwash-09" /></figure><figure><img src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Carwash-10.jpg" alt="Carwash-10" /></figure><figure><img src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Carwash-11.jpg" alt="Carwash-11" /></figure>			
												Previous
												Next
				<h3>
						Story					
				</h3>
									<p>
						Carwash app is all in one service ordering for self service kiosks. Customers simply select their types of vehicle, their desired service, make payment and get their receipt in a matter of seconds. 					</p>
				<h3>
						Features					
				</h3>
									<p>
						&#10003; Dynamic content management <br/>
&#10003; Categories for all common vehicles <br/>
&#10003; Tip feature on-off <br/>
&#10003; Installed on payment devices <br/>
					</p>
				<h3>
						Design					
				</h3>
									<p>
						&#10003; Simple and minimal UI <br/>
&#10003; Customised 5"-14" design <br/>
&#10003; Three-steps UX structure <br/>
&#10003; Dark and light themes <br/>
					</p>
															<img width="584" height="102" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Moonshire-logotype-white-1.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Moonshire-logotype-white-1.png 584w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Moonshire-logotype-white-1-300x52.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 584px) 100vw, 584px" />															
			<h2>Bakery ordering app</h2>		
			<h2>Order and pay</h2>		
								<figure><img src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Bakery-12.jpg" alt="Bakery-12" /></figure><figure><img src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Bakery-13.jpg" alt="Bakery-13" /></figure><figure><img src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Bakery-14.jpg" alt="Bakery-14" /></figure><figure><img src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Bakery-15.jpg" alt="Bakery-15" /></figure><figure><img src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Bakery-16.jpg" alt="Bakery-16" /></figure><figure><img src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Bakery-17.jpg" alt="Bakery-17" /></figure>			
												Previous
												Next
				<h3>
						Story					
				</h3>
									<p>
						Bakery’s self-service has a subtle but unique set of features and designs. Properties varied slightly from item to item and to find and order could be annoying for customers if not considered seriously. 					</p>
				<h3>
						Features					
				</h3>
									<p>
						&#10003; Dynamic content management <br/>
&#10003; Categories for groups <br/>
&#10003; Bag selection feature <br/>
					</p>
				<h3>
						Design					
				</h3>
									<p>
						&#10003; Pre-made built-in icons <br/>
&#10003; Customised 5.5"-14" design <br/>
&#10003; Two-steps UX structure <br/>
					</p>
															<img width="584" height="102" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Moonshire-logotype-white-1.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Moonshire-logotype-white-1.png 584w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Moonshire-logotype-white-1-300x52.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 584px) 100vw, 584px" />															
			<h2>General payment app</h2>		
			<h2>Scan and pay</h2>		
								<figure><img src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Pay-pos-18.jpg" alt="Pay-pos-18" /></figure><figure><img src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Pay-pos-19.jpg" alt="Pay-pos-19" /></figure><figure><img src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Pay-pos-20.jpg" alt="Pay-pos-20" /></figure><figure><img src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Pay-pos-21.jpg" alt="Pay-pos-21" /></figure><figure><img src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Pay-pos-22.jpg" alt="Pay-pos-22" /></figure><figure><img src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Pay-pos-23.jpg" alt="Pay-pos-23" /></figure>			
												Previous
												Next
				<h3>
						Story					
				</h3>
									<p>
						Many services have separate lines for ordering and checking out. With the payment app customers scan their receipt barcode and make payments after view and confirming their orders. 					</p>
				<h3>
						Features					
				</h3>
									<p>
						&#10003; Automatic price fetch <br/>
&#10003; API connection to other aps <br/>
&#10003; Multi receipt scan <br/>
					</p>
				<h3>
						Design					
				</h3>
									<p>
						&#10003; Minimal and modern UI <br/>
&#10003; Two-steps UX structure <br/>
&#10003; Responsive for small & medium sized devices <br/>
					</p>

				<h3>
						Android apps					
				</h3>
									<p>
						Android experience on mid-size screen					</p>
				<h3>
						Accessories					
				</h3>
									<p>
						Second display, info board and more					</p>
				<h3>
						Customisable					
				</h3>
									<p>
						QR, RFID, face and finger print reader					</p>

			<h2>Standard 14"</h2>		
			<h2>Multi-purpose kiosks</h2>		
			<h2>Physical properties</h2>		
					<ul>
							<li>
										Body material: Coated heet metal / plastic
									</li>
								<li>
										Standing type: 133cm x 37cm x 37cm
									</li>

									</li>
						</ul>

					<ul>

										14 LED backlit TFT IPS LCD (HD)
									</li>

									</li>

									</li>

									</li>

									</li>

									</li>

			<h2>Ordering <br/> Kiosks</h2>		
			<h2>Pastry Shop</h2>		
			<h2>Scan and pay</h2>		
			<h2>Pastry Shop</h2>		
			<h2>Scan and pay</h2>		
			<h2>Project story</h2>		
		<p>Many services have separate lines for ordering and checking out. Payment kiosks provide a self service solution for checking out the issued receipts. Customers scan their receipt barcode and make payments after view and confirming their orders. It is faster and more convenient than a cashier. </p>		
			<h2>Customer Journey</h2>

			<h2>Bus Ticket Booking</h2>		
			<h2>Pay and book</h2>		
			<h2>Bus ticket booking</h2>		
			<h2>pay and book</h2>		
			<h2>Project story</h2>		
		<p>Many reservations take place at bus terminals right before the departure. Ticket booking kiosks provide self service solutions for purchasing travel tickets in seconds. Customers can easily select their travel time and destination, and receive the printed or digital receipt. </p>		
			<h2>Customer Journey</h2>		
															<img width="1024" height="256" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/bus-journey-12-1024x256.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/bus-journey-12-1024x256.png 1024w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/bus-journey-12-300x75.png 300w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/bus-journey-12-768x192.png 768w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/bus-journey-12-1536x385.png 1536w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/bus-journey-12.png 1553w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" />

			<h2>Pharmacy Payment</h2>		
			<h2>Scan and pay</h2>		
			<h2>Pharmacy payment</h2>		
			<h2>Scan and pay</h2>		
			<h2>Project story</h2>		
		<p>Most pharmacies set separate lines for handing-in prescriptions and checking them out. Payment kiosks provide a self service solution for checking out the issued receipts in pharmacies. Customers scan their receipt barcode and make payments after confirming their scripts. It is quicker and easier than a cashier. </p>		
			<h2>Customer Journey</h2>		
															<img width="1024" height="189" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Pharmacy-journey-14-1024x189.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Pharmacy-journey-14-1024x189.png 1024w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Pharmacy-journey-14-300x55.png 300w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Pharmacy-journey-14-768x142.png 768w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Pharmacy-journey-14-1536x284.png 1536w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Pharmacy-journey-14.png 1553w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" />

			<h2>Leisure Tickets</h2>		
			<h2>Pay and pass</h2>		
			<h2>Leisure tickets</h2>		
			<h2>Pay and enter</h2>		
			<h2>Project story</h2>		
		<p>One solution does not necessarily fit every business or services. Leisure projects require customised features and design to be successful and help both businesses and customers benefit from it. What we mainly do is to maintain a balance between level of customisation and client’s budget and time frame. </p>		
			<h2>Customer Journey</h2>		
															<img width="1024" height="208" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Leisure-journey-15-1024x208.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Leisure-journey-15-1024x208.png 1024w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Leisure-journey-15-300x61.png 300w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Leisure-journey-15-768x156.png 768w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Leisure-journey-15-1536x312.png 1536w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Leisure-journey-15.png 1553w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" />

			<h2>Sanofi Diabetes</h2>		
			<h2>Watch and learn</h2>		
			<h2>Project story</h2>		
		<p>Diabetes department of Sanofi branch in the Middle East planned to have several interactive information stations at relevant clinics to empower diabetics with Sanofi’s products and latest knowledge. We developed a dedicated info kiosk that was researched and designed in collaboration with Sanofi’s knowledgable team. </p>		
			<h2>Customer Journey</h2>		
															<img width="1024" height="190" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Sanofi-journey-17-1024x190.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Sanofi-journey-17-1024x190.png 1024w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Sanofi-journey-17-300x56.png 300w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Sanofi-journey-17-768x142.png 768w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Sanofi-journey-17-1536x285.png 1536w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Sanofi-journey-17.png 1553w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" />

			<h2>Airport Check-in</h2>		
			<h2>Self-check-in kiosks</h2>		
			<h2>Airport Check-in</h2>		
			<h2>Self check-in kiosks</h2>		
			<h2>Project story</h2>		
		<p>We equipped more than 10 airports with self check-in kiosks, and carry out entire projects— from hardware and software to service and implementation. Our unique approach to product and service design differentiate the final outcome and elevate the user experience as well as business results. </p>		
			<h2>Customer Journey</h2>		
															<img width="1024" height="190" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Airport-journey-19-1024x190.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Airport-journey-19-1024x190.png 1024w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Airport-journey-19-300x56.png 300w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Airport-journey-19-768x142.png 768w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Airport-journey-19-1536x285.png 1536w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Airport-journey-19.png 1553w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" />

			<h2>Restaurant Ordering</h2>		
			<h2>Order and pay</h2>		
			<h2>Restaurant ordering</h2>		
			<h2>Order and pay</h2>		
			<h2>Project story</h2>		
		<p>Self ordering kiosks are a must-have for many hospitality businesses. Presenting visual menu, ingredients and allergens, special offers and offerings and more are among things that many customers expect and appreciate. We designed and customised various kiosks and self-service apps for ordering purposes. </p>		
			<h2>Customer Journey</h2>

			<h2>Design <br/> Process</h2>		
																<a href="#custom">
							<img width="816" height="1024" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Design-icons-dark-50-816x1024.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Design-icons-dark-50-816x1024.png 816w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Design-icons-dark-50-239x300.png 239w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Design-icons-dark-50-768x964.png 768w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Design-icons-dark-50.png 950w" sizes="(max-width: 816px) 100vw, 816px" />								</a>
			<h2>Custom <br/> Design</h2>		
															<img width="816" height="1024" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Design-icons-colored-46-816x1024.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Design-icons-colored-46-816x1024.png 816w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Design-icons-colored-46-239x300.png 239w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Design-icons-colored-46-768x964.png 768w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Design-icons-colored-46.png 950w" sizes="(max-width: 816px) 100vw, 816px" />															
															<img width="619" height="127" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Moonshire-logotype-glow-1.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Moonshire-logotype-glow-1.png 619w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Moonshire-logotype-glow-1-300x62.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 619px) 100vw, 619px" />															
			<h2>Industrial Design</h2>		
			<h2>How it looks, feels and works</h2>		
		<p>We bridge physical and digital worlds. To enable and facilitate a physical being’s experience with the digital realm, we have to consider quite a few things. Aesthetics, usability and ergonomics as well as manufacturability, maintainability and more. </p><p>Industrial Design is a discipline and expertise in which all of these factors considered, processed and delivered in an creative and innovative way. </p>		
															<img width="615" height="1024" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/industrial-design-black-1-615x1024.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/industrial-design-black-1-615x1024.png 615w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/industrial-design-black-1-180x300.png 180w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/industrial-design-black-1-768x1279.png 768w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/industrial-design-black-1.png 895w" sizes="(max-width: 615px) 100vw, 615px" />															
															<img width="627" height="1024" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/App-half-black-45-627x1024.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/App-half-black-45-627x1024.png 627w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/App-half-black-45-184x300.png 184w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/App-half-black-45-768x1255.png 768w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/App-half-black-45-940x1536.png 940w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/App-half-black-45-1253x2048.png 1253w" sizes="(max-width: 627px) 100vw, 627px" />															
															<img width="815" height="1024" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Design-icons-colored-47-815x1024.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Design-icons-colored-47-815x1024.png 815w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Design-icons-colored-47-239x300.png 239w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Design-icons-colored-47-768x965.png 768w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Design-icons-colored-47.png 949w" sizes="(max-width: 815px) 100vw, 815px" />															
															<img width="619" height="127" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Moonshire-logotype-glow-1.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Moonshire-logotype-glow-1.png 619w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Moonshire-logotype-glow-1-300x62.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 619px) 100vw, 619px" />															
			<h2>UX & UI Design</h2>		
			<h2>Back & front of digital experience</h2>		
		<p>The digital realm is boundless, flexible and connected. After bringing users into this space, we have to consider several design factors to maintain usefulness and joy of </p><p>the user experience. Learnability and usability as well as aesthetics, ergonomics, and more. User experience Design and User Interface Design are disciplines in which all of those factors explored, processed and delivered in an iterative and progressive way. </p>		
															<img width="816" height="1024" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Design-icons-colored-48-816x1024.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Design-icons-colored-48-816x1024.png 816w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Design-icons-colored-48-239x300.png 239w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Design-icons-colored-48-768x964.png 768w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Design-icons-colored-48.png 950w" sizes="(max-width: 816px) 100vw, 816px" />															
															<img width="619" height="127" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Moonshire-logotype-glow-1.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Moonshire-logotype-glow-1.png 619w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Moonshire-logotype-glow-1-300x62.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 619px) 100vw, 619px" />															
			<h2>Service Design</h2>		
			<h2>Intangible yet essential</h2>		
		<p>Since self-service solutions are at forefront of service chains, it is almost impossible not to consider and design the newly added service channel. We explore physical evidences, customer actions, front-stage actions, backstage actions and support processes. </p>		
															<img width="876" height="1536" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Service-design-dark-85-876x1536.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Service-design-dark-85-876x1536.png 876w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Service-design-dark-85-171x300.png 171w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Service-design-dark-85-584x1024.png 584w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Service-design-dark-85-768x1346.png 768w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Service-design-dark-85-1168x2048.png 1168w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Service-design-dark-85.png 1932w" sizes="(max-width: 876px) 100vw, 876px" />															
															<img width="1163" height="2048" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Process-diagram-85-1163x2048.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Process-diagram-85-1163x2048.png 1163w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Process-diagram-85-170x300.png 170w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Process-diagram-85-582x1024.png 582w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Process-diagram-85-768x1352.png 768w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Process-diagram-85-872x1536.png 872w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Process-diagram-85.png 1923w" sizes="(max-width: 1163px) 100vw, 1163px" />															
															<img width="815" height="1024" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Design-icons-colored-49-815x1024.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Design-icons-colored-49-815x1024.png 815w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Design-icons-colored-49-239x300.png 239w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Design-icons-colored-49-768x965.png 768w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Design-icons-colored-49.png 949w" sizes="(max-width: 815px) 100vw, 815px" />															
															<img width="619" height="127" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Moonshire-logotype-glow-1.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Moonshire-logotype-glow-1.png 619w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Moonshire-logotype-glow-1-300x62.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 619px) 100vw, 619px" />															
			<h2>Design Process</h2>		
			<h2>Double diamond framework</h2>		
		<p>We acquired the universally accepted Double Diamond model. It streams the problem through double diverging and converging stages to discover, define, develop and finally deliver the final solution. During this stages we empathise, define, ideate, prototype and test during some iterative processes. </p>		
			<h2>Design Tools</h2>		
			<h2>Methods we usually use for design and develop</h2>		
			<style>/*! elementor - v3.5.0 - 12-12-2021 */

			<h2>Custom Design</h2>		
			<h2>Various accessories and modules</h2>		
		<p>Self-service design is not limited to body, apps and service. There are a whole area of possibilities in technical  modules and technologies. Customised set of computing silicons, displays and printers are as imperative to define a self-service product as well as various types of scanners, payment modules and accessories. </p>		
															<img width="632" height="1024" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Custom-design-dark-632x1024.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Custom-design-dark-632x1024.png 632w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Custom-design-dark-185x300.png 185w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Custom-design-dark-768x1245.png 768w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Custom-design-dark.png 920w" sizes="(max-width: 632px) 100vw, 632px" />

<h2>Introduction</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Readymade godard brooklyn, kogi shoreditch hashtag hella shaman kitsch man bun pinterest flexitarian. Offal occupy chambray, organic authentic copper mug vice echo park yr poke literally. Ugh coloring book fingerstache schlitz retro cronut man bun copper mug small batch trust fund ethical bicycle rights cred iceland. Celiac schlitz la croix 3 wolf moon butcher. Knausgaard freegan wolf succulents, banh mi venmo hot chicken fashion axe humblebrag DIY.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Waistcoat gluten-free cronut cred quinoa. Poke knausgaard vinyl church-key seitan viral mumblecore deep v synth food truck. Ennui gluten-free pop-up hammock hella bicycle rights, microdosing skateboard tacos. Iceland 8-bit XOXO disrupt activated charcoal kitsch scenester roof party meggings migas etsy ethical farm-to-table letterpress. Banjo wayfarers chartreuse taiyaki, stumptown prism 8-bit tote bag.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>Story</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Listicle offal viral, flannel franzen roof party shoreditch meditation subway tile bicycle rights tbh fingerstache copper mug organic umami. Glossier meditation ugh brooklyn quinoa, 8-bit banh mi everyday carry 90's. Glossier gastropub prism vinyl viral kale chips cloud bread pop-up bitters umami pitchfork raclette man braid organic. Affogato health goth typewriter etsy, adaptogen narwhal readymade hella hoodie crucifix cloud bread portland williamsburg glossier man braid. Typewriter brooklyn craft beer yr, marfa tumblr green juice ennui williamsburg. Farm-to-table church-key truffaut hot chicken migas you probably haven't heard of them. Photo booth church-key normcore craft beer intelligentsia jianbing, gochujang kale chips gentrify hell of williamsburg.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>Conclusion</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Venmo fixie knausgaard readymade. 3 wolf moon blue bottle sartorial blog. Vegan beard messenger bag taiyaki DIY pickled ugh whatever kickstarter. Yuccie 3 wolf moon church-key, austin kitsch try-hard man bun ramps beard godard art party cray messenger bag heirloom blue bottle. Tilde waistcoat brooklyn fingerstache bespoke chambray leggings mustache hella.<br></p>

		<title><![CDATA[Join Zabibas Global Giveaway]]></title>
		<link>https://moonshire.co.uk/join-zabibas-global-giveaway/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2019 14:58:08 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://moonshire.co.uk/?p=35</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>Introduction</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Readymade godard brooklyn, kogi shoreditch hashtag hella shaman kitsch man bun pinterest flexitarian. Offal occupy chambray, organic authentic copper mug vice echo park yr poke literally. Ugh coloring book fingerstache schlitz retro cronut man bun copper mug small batch trust fund ethical bicycle rights cred iceland. Celiac schlitz la croix 3 wolf moon butcher. Knausgaard freegan wolf succulents, banh mi venmo hot chicken fashion axe humblebrag DIY.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Waistcoat gluten-free cronut cred quinoa. Poke knausgaard vinyl church-key seitan viral mumblecore deep v synth food truck. Ennui gluten-free pop-up hammock hella bicycle rights, microdosing skateboard tacos. Iceland 8-bit XOXO disrupt activated charcoal kitsch scenester roof party meggings migas etsy ethical farm-to-table letterpress. Banjo wayfarers chartreuse taiyaki, stumptown prism 8-bit tote bag.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>Story</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Listicle offal viral, flannel franzen roof party shoreditch meditation subway tile bicycle rights tbh fingerstache copper mug organic umami. Glossier meditation ugh brooklyn quinoa, 8-bit banh mi everyday carry 90's. Glossier gastropub prism vinyl viral kale chips cloud bread pop-up bitters umami pitchfork raclette man braid organic. Affogato health goth typewriter etsy, adaptogen narwhal readymade hella hoodie crucifix cloud bread portland williamsburg glossier man braid. Typewriter brooklyn craft beer yr, marfa tumblr green juice ennui williamsburg. Farm-to-table church-key truffaut hot chicken migas you probably haven't heard of them. Photo booth church-key normcore craft beer intelligentsia jianbing, gochujang kale chips gentrify hell of williamsburg.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>Conclusion</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Venmo fixie knausgaard readymade. 3 wolf moon blue bottle sartorial blog. Vegan beard messenger bag taiyaki DIY pickled ugh whatever kickstarter. Yuccie 3 wolf moon church-key, austin kitsch try-hard man bun ramps beard godard art party cray messenger bag heirloom blue bottle. Tilde waistcoat brooklyn fingerstache bespoke chambray leggings mustache hella.<br></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>

Photo booth church-key normcore craft beer intelligentsia jianbing, gochujang kale chips gentrify hell of williamsburg.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>Conclusion</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Venmo fixie knausgaard readymade. 3 wolf moon blue bottle sartorial blog. Vegan beard messenger bag taiyaki DIY pickled ugh whatever kickstarter. Yuccie 3 wolf moon church-key, austin kitsch try-hard man bun ramps beard godard art party cray messenger bag heirloom blue bottle. Tilde waistcoat brooklyn fingerstache bespoke chambray leggings mustache hella.<br></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title><![CDATA[Design-old]]></title>
		<link>https://moonshire.co.uk/?page_id=275</link>
		<pubDate>Thu, 18 Nov 2021 10:42:49 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Moonshire]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://moonshire.co.uk/kiosks-copy/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2><br><br>              MoonShire<br>             Design<br><br></h2>		
			<h3>Industrial Design</h3>		
		<p>What looks better works better. Doesn't it? What a self-service platfrom needs is a friendly and welcoming form-factor that invites people to come forward.</p><p>There are a lot behind good looking products and more importantantly there are a lot behind a good design. </p><p>We use design thinking method and lots of other design tools to ensure that our products, services and projects meet our clients expectations and more importantly satisfy their customers.</p>		
															<img width="400" height="980" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/kiosk-half-drawing.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/kiosk-half-drawing.png 400w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/kiosk-half-drawing-122x300.png 122w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" />															
			<h3>Double diamod method</h3>		
		<p>We use Design Thinking method and User centred approach. This means that we constantly work on everything that a project needs.</p><p>Double diamond approach consist of two divergance and convergance to find the true proplem, find the best solution, and the best way to achieve the solution.</p>		
															<img width="1024" height="540" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/double-diamond-1024x540.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/double-diamond-1024x540.jpg 1024w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/double-diamond-300x158.jpg 300w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/double-diamond-768x405.jpg 768w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/double-diamond.jpg 1358w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" />															
			<h3>Ideation</h3>		
		<p>We use sprint and agile methods as well. After define and scope the project, we use several methods to ideate and expand our minds to get closer to the solutioin area.</p><p>Our main advantage is co-design or in other words, collaborative design process which includes participation of the users, clients and expert in the design process.</p><p>Having ideas are great. But what is imperative is a systematic thinking behind it to organise and guide the team toward the best solution.</p>		
															<img width="1024" height="698" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/ideation-1-1024x698.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/ideation-1-1024x698.jpg 1024w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/ideation-1-300x205.jpg 300w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/ideation-1-768x524.jpg 768w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/ideation-1-1536x1047.jpg 1536w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/ideation-1.jpg 1980w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" />															
			<figure><a href="https://moonshire.co.uk/apps/"><img width="300" height="142" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Apps-slide-1-300x142.png" alt="" loading="lazy" /></a></figure><h3><a href="https://moonshire.co.uk/apps/">Self-service Apps</a></h3>		
			<figure><a href="https://moonshire.co.uk/kiosks/"><img width="300" height="244" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Kiosks-three-2-300x244.png" alt="" loading="lazy" /></a></figure><h3><a href="https://moonshire.co.uk/kiosks/">Self-service Kiosks</a></h3>		
			<figure><a href="https://moonshire.co.uk/design/"><img width="300" height="212" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/design-back-pink-1-300x212.png" alt="" loading="lazy" /></a></figure><h3><a href="https://moonshire.co.uk/design/">Self-service Design</a></h3>]]></content:encoded>

solution.<\/p>"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"}],"isInner":false},{"id":"ffded83","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":50,"_inline_size":68.332999999999998408384271897375583648681640625},"elements":[{"id":"ce2035b","elType":"widget","settings":{"image":{"url":"http:\/\/moonshire.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/ideation-1.jpg","id":278,"alt":"","source":"library"},"image_border_radius":{"unit":"px","top":"51","right":"51","bottom":"51","left":"51","isLinked":true},"_animation":"slideInRight"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"image"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false},{"id":"4b0d63b","elType":"section","settings":{"height":"min-height","structure":"30","margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":0,"bottom":"0","left":0,"isLinked":false}},"elements":[{"id":"ef6c0e7","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":33,"_inline_size":null},"elements":[{"id":"b78b4ea","elType":"widget","settings":{"image":{"url":"http:\/\/moonshire.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Apps-slide-1.png","id":148,"alt":"","source":"library"},"thumbnail_size":"medium","title_text":"Self-service 		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2>MoonShire Story</h2>		
			<h2>Goal</h2>		
			<h3>MoonShire Design Philosophy</h3>		
		<p>A meaningful experience is an authentic experience. It connects with your deepest idea of who you are. It doesn’t have to be epic, or impressive, or even particularly memorable. It just has to be true, for you, for those with whom you share it.</p>		
															<img width="1024" height="725" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/design-back-pink-1-1024x725.png" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/design-back-pink-1-1024x725.png 1024w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/design-back-pink-1-300x212.png 300w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/design-back-pink-1-768x544.png 768w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/design-back-pink-1.png 1100w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" />															
			<h2>Team</h2>		
		<p>We have multidisciplinary team. from customer insight, to design and app development.</p>		
															<img width="1024" height="196" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/team-icons-1024x196.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/team-icons-1024x196.jpg 1024w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/team-icons-300x57.jpg 300w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/team-icons-768x147.jpg 768w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/team-icons-1536x293.jpg 1536w, https://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/team-icons-2048x391.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" />															
			<figure><a href="https://moonshire.co.uk/apps/"><img width="300" height="142" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Apps-slide-1-300x142.png" alt="" loading="lazy" /></a></figure><h3><a href="https://moonshire.co.uk/apps/">Self-service Apps</a></h3>		
			<figure><a href="https://moonshire.co.uk/kiosks/"><img width="300" height="244" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Kiosks-three-2-300x244.png" alt="" loading="lazy" /></a></figure><h3><a href="https://moonshire.co.uk/kiosks/">Self-service Kiosks</a></h3>		
			<figure><a href="https://moonshire.co.uk/design/"><img width="300" height="212" src="http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/design-back-pink-1-300x212.png" alt="" loading="lazy" /></a></figure><h3><a href="https://moonshire.co.uk/design/">Self-service Design</a></h3>]]></content:encoded>

		<content:encoded><![CDATA[http://moonshire.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Logo-motion-6-2.m4v#t=,3		
			<style>/*! elementor - v3.5.0 - 12-12-2021 */
.elementor-heading-title{padding:0;margin:0;line-height:1}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title[class*=elementor-size-]>a{color:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-small{font-size:15px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-medium{font-size:19px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-large{font-size:29px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xl{font-size:39px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xxl{font-size:59px}</style><h2>MoonShire</h2>		
			<h2>Story</h2>		
			<h2>Design first</h2>		
		<p>There is no meaning to technology without a connection to human needs. Our passion and focus is on designing solutions and experiences through technology. Design is our way to contribute to society toward a more enjoyable and productive life for everyone. </p>		
			<h2>Customer first</h2>		
		<p>Our tool is design, our focus is customer experience. We share your passion and responsibility toward your customers and the values you deliver to them. We help to get insights, define opportunities, design and implement service solutions tailored to your customers. </p>		
			<h2>Client first</h2>		
		<p>MoonShire clients are quality service providers who welcome technology and new ideas into their service lines and business forefronts. They are what we call forerunners. We admire their passions and efforts, and help them to achieve more in their revered way. </p>		
			<h2>Who we are?</h2>		
			<h2>A group of creatives who happen to reinvent kiosk</h2>
